# 3. MICRONUTRIENTS (CHELATED FORMS) {#micronutrients-chelated-forms-1}

**Replacement Value: \$27-\$48 per tonne CFI⁷⁹**

CFI delivers six essential micronutrients in naturally chelated and
organic-bound forms: iron (Fe), zinc (Zn), manganese (Mn), copper (Cu),
boron (B) and molybdenum (Mo). These are supplied in small but highly
effective quantities that are expensive to replace with synthetic
products---especially in tropical, alkaline or highly leached soils
where conventional micronutrient salts often fail.⁷⁹

Across Fe, Zn, Mn, Cu, B and Mo, 1 tonne of CFI provides \~0.66-1.22 kg
of micronutrients, with an equivalent synthetic replacement value of
\$27-\$48 per tonne CFI.⁷⁹

