**3.2.1 Magnesium - 3-5 kg Mg - Replacement Value \$5-11**

**3.2.1.1 What is in CFI?**

One tonne of CFI contains about 3-5 kg of magnesium, mainly from BSF
larvae and chicken manure. In these materials, Mg is held inside
proteins, enzymes and organic complexes, rather than as free mineral
salts. As microbes decompose the organic matter, Mg is released
gradually into the soil solution instead of arriving all at once.⁹¹

**3.2.1.2 Synthetic Replacement Cost - Kieserite Benchmark**

Standard Mg fertiliser for plantations in Indonesia is kieserite
(MgSO₄·H₂O), typically about 27% MgO (\~16% Mg) and 22% S.⁸⁹

**To match the Mg in 1 tonne of CFI:**

> • Low Mg case (3 kg): 3 kg ÷ 0.16 ≈ 19 kg kieserite
>
> • High Mg case (5 kg): 5 kg ÷ 0.16 ≈ 31 kg kieserite

Non-subsidised kieserite in Indonesia is commonly sold in 50 kg bags at
an effective price around \$240-360 per tonne of product.⁸⁹ That is
\$0.24-0.36 per kg kieserite, or roughly \$1.5-2.2 per kg Mg nutrient.

**Indicative replacement cost for Mg in 1 tonne of CFI:**

> • Low side: 19 kg × \$0.24 ≈ \$5 / t CFI
>
> • High side: 31 kg × \$0.35 ≈ \$11 / t CFI

**3.2.1.3 CFI vs Synthetic Magnesium - The Organic Advantage**

Kieserite is a pure mineral salt that dissolves quickly, giving a short,
intense pulse of Mg²⁺ and SO₄²⁻. On sandy or highly weathered tropical
soils, this pulse can leach beyond the root zone rapidly.⁹²

**By contrast, Mg in CFI:⁹³**

> • Is co-delivered with organic matter, increasing cation exchange
> capacity (CEC) in the topsoil
>
> • Is released gradually as BSF biomass and manure decompose
>
> • Arrives together with N, S, Ca, chitin and micronutrients,
> stimulating roots and microbes

# 3.3. PROTEIN VALUE

CFI contains 271.2 kg of protein per tonne (27.12% crude protein),
providing both feed-style economic value and agronomic value when
applied to soil. This section quantifies the protein replacement value
using global benchmark ingredients and then summarises the additional
organic matter benefits that synthetic fertilizers cannot provide.⁹⁴

