> (Valuates Reports)

*Market Composition: Organo-mineral fertilizers combine 20-40% organic
matter with mineral nutrients (nitrogen, phosphorus, potassium),
offering controlled nutrient release and enhanced soil health. Despite
representing less than 2% of the total fertilizer market, these products
command 30-50% price premiums.¹³⁵*

