**5.6.2 China Market Specifics**

China\'s organic fertilizer market benefits from strong government
support through the \'Zero Growth in Chemical Fertilizer Use by 2020\'
policy (achieved) and the new \'2025 Organic Priority\' directive
requiring 30% organic matter in all fertilizers.¹⁵³

> • Organic fertilizer production: 20 million MT annually
>
> • Government subsidies: RMB 2,000-3,000/ha for organic conversion
>
> • Target: 40% reduction in chemical fertilizer use by 2030

