**6.1 Executive Summary - Trial Results**

The UGACOF/Sucafina field trials conducted in Uganda (2020-2022) provide
definitive proof that Marula Proteen\'s BSF-based fertilizer outperforms
all alternatives in coffee production. The trials compared four
fertilization strategies across 36 plots with rigorous scientific
methodology.¹⁶⁵

***Key Result: Marula Proteen BSF fertilizer achieved the highest yields
(3.6 tons/ha) at the lowest cost (\$220/ha), generating \$1,951/ha
profit compared to just \$482/ha for imported organic and \$736/ha for
synthetic NPK fertilizers.¹⁶⁶***

