**6.7 Coffee Fertilization Requirements**

**6.7.1 Nutrient Removal Rates**

Coffee plants have specific nutrient requirements based on variety and
yield targets:¹⁸³

> • Nitrogen (N): 1 kg N needed to produce 10 kg coffee berries
>
> • Target application: 200 kg N/ha for 2,000 kg/ha yield target
>
> • Arabica removal: 34 kg N, 5 kg P₂O₅, 45 kg K₂O per ton clean coffee
>
> • Robusta removal: 35 kg N, 7 kg P₂O₅, 39 kg K₂O per ton clean coffee

