**Industry Scale and Waste Generation:²⁵⁰**

• Total processing capacity: 38,500 MT/month

• Heads and shells waste: 15,400 MT/month (40% of input)

• Species: Litopenaeus vannamei (70%), Penaeus monodon (30%)

• Chitin content: 15-25% of dry shell weight

• Protein content: 20-43% of dry weight

• Calcium carbonate: 20-40% of dry weight

