## 8.1.3 CSRD Reporting Timeline

The Corporate Sustainability Reporting Directive fundamentally alters
palm oil procurement requirements through mandatory Scope 3 emissions
disclosure^²⁵⁶^. Wave 1 companies are already requesting
supplier-specific emission factors, creating immediate demand for
traceable, low-emission palm oil products^²⁵⁷^.

