**Europe\'s Palm Oil Leadership:**

-   Europe consumes 45% of global certified sustainable palm oil
    [rspo](https://rspo.org/new-report-shows-europe-is-the-biggest-market-for-sustainable-palm-oil/)

-   Netherlands serves as EU gateway - Rotterdam/Amsterdam ports are
    central entry

-   Strong re-export network - much palm oil is processed and
    re-exported within EU

