# 10.1 LIDAR VOLUMETRIC MEASUREMENT SYSTEM

Industrial-grade LiDAR (Light Detection and Ranging) technology provides
continuous, accurate measurement of waste volumes at collection points
and processing facilities. This revolutionary approach eliminates the
±20-50% error rates common in manual surveys while providing real-time
digital evidence for carbon credit verification. The system\'s 360° ×
270° field of view and 300,000 points per second capture rate ensure
comprehensive coverage of irregular waste piles, enabling precise
volumetric calculations essential for emissions baseline establishment.

