³ Validation & Registry Listing (Months 6--10): \$46,000--\$65,000; VVB
validation audit \$20,000--\$35,000 (3--5 days onsite); Verra registry
fees \$5,000--\$10,000; PDD final edits \$5,000--\$8,000; stakeholder
documentation \$2,000--\$5,000; travel \$10,000--\$15,000. Range
reflects VVB audit complexity and travel requirements.

⁴ MRV Setup & Registration (Months 10--14): \$40,000--\$62,000;
monitoring equipment (meters, sensors, lab gear) \$15,000--\$25,000; lab
protocol development \$5,000--\$8,000; staff training \$3,000--\$5,000;
calibration & startup \$5,000--\$8,000; registration admin
\$3,000--\$5,000; documentation \$2,000--\$3,000; travel
\$2,000--\$5,000. Equipment costs vary by sourcing (local vs.
international suppliers).

⁵ Verification & Issuance (Months 14--24): \$38,000--\$58,000; VVB
verification audit \$15,000--\$25,000; data QA & report
\$5,000--\$10,000; issuance fees (Verra, \~\$0.02--0.05/credit for
151,200 credits) \$3,000--\$7,500; travel \$5,000--\$10,000; legal/admin
\$2,000--\$5,000; contingency \$3,000--\$5,000. Includes 8-month
pre-verification readiness phase.

⁶ Annual M&V Ongoing (Year 2+): \$30,000--\$45,000/year; data collection
& compilation \$5,000--\$8,000; lab testing \$3,000--\$5,000; equipment
maintenance \$2,000--\$4,000; reporting \$3,000--\$5,000; VVB annual
verification \$10,000--\$15,000; registry fees \$2,000--\$3,000;
consultant support \$5,000--\$10,000. Recurring cycle for 10+ years of
project operation.

⁷ ERPA Upfront Financing: Standard practice in voluntary carbon markets;
10--30% upfront payment common; 20% upfront at \$20/tCO₂e on 151,200
tCO₂e/yr = \$604,800 example. ERPA timing: typically signed Months 4--6
during advanced PDD stage, upfront payment received within 30 days of
