  Product**     Composition**               C**         
  ------------- --------------------------- ----------- --------------------
  Rinnova       Organic N fertilizer -- N   \~30% C     High-N micropellets
                9% (no P/K). From manure &              for top-dressing in
                feather meal; slow N                    organic systems
                release.                                (cereals)

