**15.1 Executive Summary**

This section provides a comprehensive overview of grant and financing
opportunities available to CFI for its BSF waste valorization technology
during 2025--2026. The funding landscape includes both grant programmes
for early-stage development and institutional financing mechanisms for
scale-up operations.

CFI\'s technology---converting agricultural waste (EFB, PKF) into
premium organic fertilizer while avoiding methane emissions---aligns
exceptionally well with multiple EU and international funding priorities
including circular economy, climate mitigation, and sustainable
agriculture.

**Total Addressable Funding**

The combined funding opportunities identified in this section represent
over €50 million in potential grant funding and €500+ million in
institutional financing through EIB/EIF mechanisms. CFI should pursue a
portfolio approach, targeting 3--4 complementary grants while preparing
for institutional financing at scale-up phase.

