and O&M framework, and a stakeholder engagement and capacity building
plan.

**Strategic Alignment**

ADB\'s Indonesia Country Partnership Strategy 2025--2029 prioritizes
green, inclusive, and resilient growth with specific focus on circular
economy practices, climate action, and sustainable agriculture. CFI\'s
EFB/PKF methane-avoidance project directly supports Indonesia\'s NDC
commitments and aligns with ADB\'s \$500 million policy-based loan for
reducing marine debris through improved waste management.

